lead_paragraph: Heavy rain washed out much of the third day's play of the second test between Pakistan and New Zealand on Sunday, with the hosts facing just one ball in their second innings before bad light ended proceedings.

headline.print_headline: New Zealand Ahead After Rainy Third Day Against Pakistan
headline.main: New Zealand Ahead After Rainy Third Day Against Pakistan
